    "description": "MEEQ Inc. engages in the mobile IoT support business in Japan. It offers MEEQ, a mobile data communication service for IoT that allows to purchase and manage multiple lines from a console screen, as well as provides databases and data processing for creating IoT systems without coding or system development. The company's services include MEEQ Data Platform, which collects and processes data from IoT devices; MEEQ AI, a data processing SaaS that uses AI to process data collected and stored from IoT devices; MEEQ SIM, a IoT communications solutions; MEEQ Global SIM; MEEQ service integration, which links data in IoT storage with linked services; and MEEQ Business Tools that provides various business functions necessary for running an IoT business. MEEQ Inc. was formerly known as Sony Network Communications Smart Platform Inc. and changed its name to MEEQ Inc. in December 2022. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
